        "message": "Always use NifmServiceType_User. This should stop crashes when used together ldn_mitm\n\nNifm provides only two admin session. Ldn_mitm needs one, previously we also used one, this caused qlaunch to crash when opening wifi settings as it attempted to open its legitimate session.\nSince we only need to retrieve the IP address we can use nifm:u just fine which should solve this crash.",
