        "date": "2025-05-05T07:55:02Z",
        "message": "grammar fix pt-BR.json (#348)\n\n* grammar fix pt-BR.json\n\n* changed \"estã instalado\" to \"está instalado\" (\"estã\" does not exist, \"está\" is the correct form.)\r\n\r\n* changed \"reproduzí-los\" to \"reproduzi-los\" (incorrect accent).\r\n\r\n* changed \"Isto\" to \"Isso\" (\"Isso\" is most commonly used in brazilian portuguese.)\n\n* pt and pt-br translation to new sysmodule strings\n\n* portuguese and brazilian portuguese translation for the new sysmodule strings used for an upcoming feature\n\n* spanish translation for new sysmodule strings\n\n* for european spanish\n\n* also fixed one typo from portuguese.json",
        "url": "https://github.com/exelix11/SysDVR/commit/c557be515e5877b799d3b983a38f661a7a2386ca"
    },
